It parses a plate number from the JPG/PNG picture. It utilizes the [Total.js Platenumber API](https://docs.totaljs.com/totalapi/6c221003eo51c/#13ffb001db51d).

__Input data:__
```js
// {String} dataURI of an image
'data:image/jpeg;base64,/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQEB....'
```

__Output data:__
```js
[
  {
    "value": "H786P0J",
    "confidence": 89.8356
  },
  {
    "value": "H786POJ",
    "confidence": 87.6114
  },
  {
    "value": "HN786P0J",
    "confidence": 85.2152
  }
]
```

The component splits a message with an array of objects on the input into separate messages with individual objects on the output.

